quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  54,9,"Abandu ba Nuh bakhaya bo nibashili, nibayingasia\tOmusumba\twefu, nibamuboolela mbu nomulalu mana nibamwalabila.(nibamululila)"
  54,10,"Mana nasaba Nyasaye wuwe; naboola mbu: Toto esie ekhailwe, kho habine"
  54,11,Mana nikhwikula emiliango chomwikulu khu maatsi kayombokhanga
  54,12,"Ne nikhufutula liloba nikhukhola emialo (emichela), amatsi nikabukanana khulikhuwa liali niliburire"
  54,13,Ne nikhubachinga khushietsimbao nende imikoye. (Isafina)
  54,14,"Yatsitsanga nikhuyihenga, okhuba ni omurungo khu kalia kabamuingasinjia"
  54,15,"Ne toto bwene khwachikhola okhuba eshimanyisio, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,16,"kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie, nende okhwikannyilisia khwanje"
  54,17,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu okhumanya, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,18,"Babu A’di bakhaya, kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje"
  54,19,Toto efwekhwabarumila omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka khutsinyanga tsimbi tsilondokhaane
  54,20,Nikusiula Abandu opara mbu nebisichiri biemisala chisiulilwe
  54,21,Mana eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende amekanyilisio kanje
  54,22,"Netoto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu okhuyimanya, Ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,23,Abandu ba Thamudi bayingasia Abekanyilisi
  54,24,"Nibaboola mbu : “Khuloonde Omundu namundu urula mwifwe, efwe mana khuba khulaba mubokori bwahabulalu.”"
  54,25,Niye butswa yenyene okhurula mwifwe wamakanyiliso keshela ? halali uno nomubeyi omukhongo omufuru
  54,26,Nibamanye mutsuli niwina umubeeyi omukhongo omufuru
  54,27,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhubarumila ingamia ikhasi kulwa okhubatema, mana obahenge butswa mana wifwile"
  54,28,"Ne baboolele mbu amatsi kalakabulwamwo hakari wabu, balakabukhasibwa khulwa okhukanywa"
  54,29,"Mana nibalaanga Omundu wabu, niyetsa nayisinza"
  54,30,Ne eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje
  54,31,"Toto efwe khwabarumila oluyoka lulala lwonyene, nibabashinga abitiisi biokhumbashila olukaka"
  54,32,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani okhuba Inyangu, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,33,Abandu ba Lut bayingasia abekanyilisi
  54,34,"Toto efwe khwabarumila eshifulumutu shiamachina halali abaloondi ba Lut, khwabahabina mumabwibwi"
  54,35,"Tsimbabasi okhurulu khwifwe, Endio nilwakhurunganga ulia ukhupanga orio muno"
  54,36,"Ne toto yabekanyilisilia eshinyasio shiefu, halali bo bali netsinganakani khumekanyilisio ako"
  54,37,"Ne toto benya mbu abahelesie abacheni be, mana nikhubawofusia tsimoni tsiabu , nikhubaboolela mbu: “pile eshinyasio shianje namekanyilisio.”"
  54,38,Ne toto shiabeeshela eshinyasio shitsilila mumabwibi
  54,39,Kho mana pile eshinyasio shianje namekanyilisio
  54,40,"Netoto khwakhola Ikurani okhuba inyangu, ne koo khiliwo nende witsulila"
  54,41,Netoto Abekanyilisi betsela Abandu ba Firaun
  54,42,"Bakhaya ebimanyisio biefu biosi pe, mana nikhubatila omutilo kwa amaani kwobunyali"
  54,43,Ne Abakhayi benyu bali nende amani okhushila abo baranjilila nohomba kahandikwa mubitabu mbu enywe mubule okhufunaanibwa
  54,44,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: ‘‘efwe khuli abaanji khulishila butswa.’’"
  54,45,Abanji abo balashilwa ne balakalukha inyuma tsimbilo
  54,46,"Halali inyanga yeyindukho niyabalakwa, Ne indukho ni isiro muno mana khandi indulu pa"
  54,47,Toto Abetsimbi balimubukori nende mubulalu
  54,48,"Inyanga yabaliswerululwa mafumama nibasukunwa mumulilo, baliboolelwa mbu : ‘‘pile omulilo kwa Jahanam.’’"
  54,49,Ne toto buli eshindu khwaloonga khushichelo
  54,50,"Ne likhuwa liefu nililala butwa, shinga okhulimba no khulimbula tsimoni"
  54,51,Ne toto khwasishia abashienywe alikho mwinywe uparanga
  54,52,Ne koosi kabakhola kali mubitabu
  54,53,Liosi liosi lititi nende likhonga liahandikwa
  54,54,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda chilimwo emialo
  54,55,"Mushikhalo shiatoto, ewo Omwami Omunyali"